  "detailed_description": "It is said that riches beyond imagination lay at the bottom of the dungeon of Faveg.<br>Driven by greed, adventurers flock there to meet their ends.<br>Will you be better than them?<br><br>Brave the hordes of monsters below as you train your party in this Roguelike take on class based progression.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/aabe50e10917641e646501f62c263544.webp?t=1731951652\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>Every level up a decision, try to build competent fighters with semi-random class choices every level.<br>Certain class combinations will open up new growth paths for a character to take, try to find them all!<br>Will you build a wild berserker, a powerful wizard, a devout priest, or something in between?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/153677c0ce874e58b6ce1c2c94b63071.avif?t=1731951652\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/d096a7d4f594d2d95fc126aac4bf0630.webp?t=1731951652\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>Choose between hundreds of active and passive skills to grant your party an edge in battle!<br>Only 12 can be active at a time though, so think twice before swapping.<br>Will you carry powerful attacks, tide-turning buffs, or passives to improve your other skills?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/Savagery_Size.PNG?t=1731951652\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/0bad97c0b516238af634f106a42076a5.webp?t=1731951652\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>7 floors full of danger await you, each one more hostile than the last.<br>Every fight will pose a different challenge, can you overcome every single one, or will your strategy crumble?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/3986b279752d77f049dc2d3336cf8ab5.poster.avif?t=1731951652\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/3986b279752d77f049dc2d3336cf8ab5.webm?t=1731951652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/3986b279752d77f049dc2d3336cf8ab5.mp4?t=1731951652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "It is said that riches beyond imagination lay at the bottom of the dungeon of Faveg.<br>Driven by greed, adventurers flock there to meet their ends.<br>Will you be better than them?<br><br>Brave the hordes of monsters below as you train your party in this Roguelike take on class based progression.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/aabe50e10917641e646501f62c263544.webp?t=1731951652\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>Every level up a decision, try to build competent fighters with semi-random class choices every level.<br>Certain class combinations will open up new growth paths for a character to take, try to find them all!<br>Will you build a wild berserker, a powerful wizard, a devout priest, or something in between?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/153677c0ce874e58b6ce1c2c94b63071.avif?t=1731951652\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/d096a7d4f594d2d95fc126aac4bf0630.webp?t=1731951652\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>Choose between hundreds of active and passive skills to grant your party an edge in battle!<br>Only 12 can be active at a time though, so think twice before swapping.<br>Will you carry powerful attacks, tide-turning buffs, or passives to improve your other skills?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/Savagery_Size.PNG?t=1731951652\" /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/0bad97c0b516238af634f106a42076a5.webp?t=1731951652\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>7 floors full of danger await you, each one more hostile than the last.<br>Every fight will pose a different challenge, can you overcome every single one, or will your strategy crumble?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/3986b279752d77f049dc2d3336cf8ab5.poster.avif?t=1731951652\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/3986b279752d77f049dc2d3336cf8ab5.webm?t=1731951652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152330/extras/3986b279752d77f049dc2d3336cf8ab5.mp4?t=1731951652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
